Welcome to Equidox: PDF Remediation Tool
The Equidox applicationLinks to an external site. is a web-based tool for remediating PDF documents, designed for ease of use without requiring advanced knowledge of accessibility or expertise in Adobe PDF structure. Currently utilized by some campuses, a proposal for system-wide licensing has been proposed. The plan includes 72 shared licenses across campuses, allowing unlimited user accounts but limiting simultaneous users to 72. This initiative, once in trial, aims to support campuses in implementing their PDF remediation plans effectively.

Why Use Equidox?
Compliance: Helps organizations meet legal requirements for digital accessibility, reducing the risk of lawsuits.
Efficiency: Automated tools and AI features significantly reduce the time and effort required to make PDFs accessible.
Inclusivity: Ensures that digital documents are usable by everyone, including individuals who rely on assistive technologies.
Reputation: Demonstrates a commitment to corporate social responsibility and inclusivity, which can enhance an organization's public image
